OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright and
OL,6,Fsunny end to the afternoon. Staying
OL,7,Fdry overnight with some patchy cloud
OL,8,Faround. Another warm night for many,
OL,9,Fespecially in urban areas and cities,
OL,10,Fwhile rural locations become
OL,11,Fnoticeably cooler. Light wind
OL,12,Fthroughout.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FAnother hot day, Dry and
OL,15,Fpredominantly sunny to end the week.
OL,16,FFeeling hot in many places with cooler
OL,17,Fconditions along coastal areas, with
OL,18,Fan onshore breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
