OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstarts to Saturday and Sunday but
OL,7,Fcloud burning back with sunny spells
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Dry with plenty
OL,9,Fof sunshine on Monday. Cooler this
OL,10,Fweekend but remaining above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
